%% Decision after receiving response
5:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Continue|6:task:(Book Tour)
5:exclusivegateway:{x} --> |Do not continue|15:endevent:(((endevent)))

6:task:(Book Tour) --> 7:exclusivegateway:{x}

